trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint> maintains two <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocationCollection> objects: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.MatchingLocations%2A> specifies parameters used for matching activity status events and <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.ExcludedLocations%2A> specifies parameters used to exclude activity status events from matching.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint> mantiene dos objetos <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocationCollection>: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.MatchingLocations%2A> especifica parámetros utilizados para encontrar coincidencias con eventos de estado de actividad y <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.ExcludedLocations%2A> especifica parámetros utilizados para excluir eventos de estado de actividad de la búsqueda de coincidencias.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocationCollection" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa una nueva instancia de la clase <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocationCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocationCollection" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa una nueva instancia de la clase <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocationCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: The default constructor initializes the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocationCollection> to an empty list.
trans-unit.target: El constructor predeterminado inicializa <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocationCollection> en una lista vacía.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocationCollection" /> class by using a list of user locations.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa una instancia nueva de la clase <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocationCollection" /> con una lista de ubicaciones de usuario.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocationCollection> is initialized to contain the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocation> objects specified in `locations`.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocationCollection> se inicializa para contener los objetos <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocation> especificados en `locations`.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="locations" /> is a null reference (<see langword="Nothing" /> in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="locations" /> es una referencia nula (<see langword="Nothing" /> en Visual Basic).
